text: #Thanksgiving Conservation Tip: After frying your turkey refrain from pouring grease down the drain. It can create clogs in our sewer pipes! text: #Thanksgiving Conservation Tip: After you fry up the turkey, refrain from pouring grease down the drain. It creates clogs in our sewer pipes! To properly dispose of #FOG (fats, oils & grease), let it cool and place it in a bag for disposal in your trash container @TalkingTrashPHX pic.twitter.com/0ZDIt6qAGu
text_html: #Thanksgiving Conservation Tip: After you fry up the turkey, refrain from pouring grease down the drain. It creates clogs in our sewer pipes! To properly dispose of #FOG (fats, oils & grease), let it cool and place it in a bag for disposal in your trash container @TalkingTrashPHX pic.twitter.com/0ZDIt6qAGu
